snippet.title: Disgaea 1 Complete - Earth's Mightiest Heroes?! (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
...and Gordon, too!

Learn more @ disgaea.us/d1c
Pre-order today! http://bit.ly/D1Complete

The OVERLORD of strategy RPGs returns! Join Laharl, Etna, and Flonne in their crazy adventure through the Netherworld to crown a new Overlord. Remastered for a new generation, with brand new visuals! Meet the angels of Celestia, who have sent Flonne down to the Netherworld to assassinate King Krichevskoy. But, upon realizing that the King was already dead, she decides to join Laharl and gang...
